graph LR
    CodeFlare[CodeFlare Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    CodeFlare -->|requires<br/>CRD provider| KubeRay[KubeRay Operator v1.2.1]
    CodeFlare -->|requires<br/>cert rotation| CertController[cert-controller v0.12.0]
    CodeFlare -->|requires<br/>platform| Kubernetes[Kubernetes 1.31+]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    CodeFlare -.->|optional<br/>batch scheduling| Kueue[Kueue v0.10.1+]
    CodeFlare -.->|optional<br/>OAuth + Routes| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.11+]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    CodeFlare -->|reads config| ODHOperator[ODH Operator]
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|creates CRs via UI| CodeFlare

    %% Integration Points
    CodeFlare -->|watches/creates| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrapes metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP| CodeFlare

    %% Managed Resources
    CodeFlare -->|creates| RayResources[Ray Cluster Resources:<br/>- OAuth Proxy<br/>- Routes/Ingress<br/>- NetworkPolicies<br/>- Services<br/>- Secrets]
    CodeFlare -->|manages| AppWrapperResources[AppWrapper Resources:<br/>- Jobs<br/>- Deployments<br/>- StatefulSets<br/>- PyTorchJobs]

    %% External Services
    CodeFlare -.->|ray clusters access| S3[S3 Storage<br/>HTTPS/443]

    %% CRDs Watched
    RayClusterCR[RayCluster CR<br/>ray.io/v1] -->|watched by| CodeFlare
    AppWrapperCR[AppWrapper CR<br/>workload.codeflare.dev/v1beta2] -->|watched by| CodeFlare

    %% Kueue integration
    Kueue -.->|updates status| AppWrapperCR

    %% Base cluster management
    KubeRay -->|manages base cluster| RayClusterCR

